com.foreach.across.modules.entity.query.support

Class EntityQueryAuthenticationFunctions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.entity.query.support.EntityQueryAuthenticationFunctions
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EntityQueryFunctionHandler

    public class EntityQueryAuthenticationFunctions
extends Object
implements EntityQueryFunctionHandler
    Contains Spring security related entity query functions:
    • currentUser(): returns the principal name of the current authenticated principal
    Supported property type is String.

    Note that if there is no principal authenticated this function will throw an exception.

    Since:
    2.0.0
    Author:
    Arne Vandamme
